<body>
<div type="letter">
  <pb facs="1038110" n="1"/>  
  <opener>Ad <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119112450">Jacobum Her<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>um</rs>, <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavium</rs>.</opener>
  <p>Acceptissim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> mihi fuerunt nuper<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> <rs type="letter" key="B_991170516908905501">liter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs>, quibus felicem <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_ME943KC7">Disputationis</rs> successum mihi
  <lb/>gratulari, studiisque meis ulteriorem Dei benedictionem animitus apprecari dignatus es; gratias proin
  <lb/>Tibi ago maximas, quod non solum enixam in me voluntatem sinceris votis mihi testari, sed et deper<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ditis <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>quod maxime doleo<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> prioribus quas ad me dedisti <rs type="letter">literis</rs><!-- ToDo: Nachgewiesener Brief. Im BIBB erfassen und verlinken --> Amicitiam Tuam, quam magni semper
  <lb/>feci et porro faciam, iterata scriptione confirmare volueris. Gratularis mihi de su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>o omnium ap<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>plausu, de quo sane gloriari non possum, nostrates enim, ut Tu ipse nosti, res insolitas et quas non
  <lb/>intelligunt, cujusmodi est calculus <rs type="keyword">algebraicus</rs>, ne dicam <rs type="keyword">infinite parvorum</rs>, in materiis <rs type="keyword">Juridicis</rs>
  <lb/>adhibitus, risu potius quam applausu excipere sunt soliti. Propositum mihi fuit primitus tractare
    <lb/>materiam mere Juridicam, sed <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_ME943KC7">Dissertationem Mathematico-Juridicam</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me postulare videbatur om<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nium expectatio, cui hac saltem in re satisfaciendum esse duxi; suspicabantur autem, me non aliud,
  <lb/>quam leve illud, quod jam alii, qui sibi magni videbantur esse Mathematici, pertractarunt, <hi rend="u">de con<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>troversiis limitum</hi> argumentum electurum esse, non credentes usum Matheseos in <rs type="keyword">Jure</rs> etiam hucus<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
  <lb/>se extendere, quamobrem non dubito, quin <choice><abbr>ICti</abbr><expan>Juris Consulti</expan></choice> nostri dilectam nostram Mathesin perspecta ejus
    <lb/>multifaria utilitate posthac minus contemturi sint. De tradito <abbr>Rev.</abbr> tuo <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1048628825">Parenti</rs> uno <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_ME943KC7">Dissertatio<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nis</rs> exemplari non est quod gratias agas, illud Te jam accepisse spero una cum fasciculo, quem Tibi
    <lb/>mitti curavit <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruus</rs> meus, et cui ego adjunxi aliquot <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_ME943KC7">Dissertationis</rs> me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> exemplaria <rs type="persons">Amicis</rs>,
  <lb/>si qui sunt harum rerum cupidi, distribuenda. Gratum erit, si de hoc meo et altero Artis Conje<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ctandi specimine, quod <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117601020">Remondus de Montmort</rs> edidit libro, cui titulus <hi rend="u"><rs type="biblio" key="biblio_B9DV33K8">Essai d'Analyse sur les
    <pb facs="1038112" n="2"/>
  <lb/>Jeux de Hazard</rs></hi> judicium Tuum expones, et pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sertim quid sentias de Problematibus ab <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117601020">Auctore</rs> in
    <lb/>fine <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_B9DV33K8">libri</rs> propositis. Litem quam de <rs type="keyword">spatiis H<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>perbolicis</rs> plusquam <rs type="keyword">infintis</rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118771167">Wallisio</rs> movet <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119062372">Varigno<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nius</rs> refutandus, ut scribis, <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <abbr>P.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118937669">Guidone Grando</rs>, puto ex parte meram esse Logomachiam; non negabit
  <lb/><figure facs="../images/figures/1038112_01.png" hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"/> enim <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119062372">Varignonius</rs>, spatium infinitum <formula>BACKI</formula> conte<add>n</add>tum inter <rs type="keyword">Asymptotos</rs> <formula>AB</formula>, <formula>AC</formula>, et
  <lb/><rs type="keyword">H<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>perbolam</rs> quamvis <formula>IK</formula> <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>sola, ni fallor, excepta h<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>perbola ordinaria<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> infinities
  <lb/>minus esse spatio <formula>BACHF</formula> (comprehenso ab iisdem As<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>mptotis <formula>AB</formula>, <formula>AC</formula>, et H<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>perbola
  <lb/><formula>FH</formula> uno gradu altiori quam pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cedens <formula>IK</formula>) nec non quolibet ejus segmento <formula>BADEF</formula>,
  <lb/>adeoque hoc respectu spatium istud curvilineum <formula>BADEF</formula> <hi rend="u">plusquam infinitum</hi>, et
  <lb/>rationem ejus ad parallelogra<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>um inscriptum <formula>ADEG</formula> <hi rend="u">plusquam infinitam</hi>
    <lb/>dici posse, utut contrarium dicere videatur in fine <rs type="biblio" key="bibl_MDEJADS3">schedias<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>matis</rs> his verbis: <foreign xml:lang="fre"><cit><quote><hi rend="u">D'où l'on voit...</hi></quote></cit></foreign> ubi etiam illud miror, quod
  <lb/>explodat <hi rend="u">plusquam infinita</hi>, admittat vero talia infinita quo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum alterum altero <hi rend="u">magis infinitum sit</hi>. <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118771167">Wallisium</rs> tamen dupliciter falli credo, primum in eo quod
  <lb/>spatia h<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>perbolica <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>que ac complementa <rs type="keyword">parabolica</rs> ad <rs type="keyword">parallelogra<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>a</rs> inscripta vel circumscripta <abbr>h. e.</abbr>
  <lb/><formula>\int ydx</formula> ad <formula>xy</formula> in Curvis, quarum generalis <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quatio est <formula>x^{m}=y</formula>, rationem habere putat ut 1 ad <formula>m+1</formula>; <rs type="keyword">integra<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>le</rs> enim absolutum ipsius <formula>ydx</formula> non est <formula>\frac{x^{m+1}}{m+1}</formula> sed <formula>\frac{x^{m+1}-0^{m+1}}{m+1}</formula>,<note type="editorial">Im Zähler wurde ein Pluszeichen durch ein Minuszeichen überschrieben.<!-- ToDo: Kontrollieren ob im Zähler 0 oder o gelesen werden soll. --></note> evanescente quidem in parabolis po<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>steriori membro <formula>\frac{-0^{m+1}}{m+1}</formula><!-- ToDo: Kontrollieren ob im Zähler 0 oder o gelesen werden soll. -->, quod autem in h<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>perbolis, ubi <formula>m</formula> est numerus negativus, fit <formula>=\frac{\infty^{-m-1}}{-m-1}</formula>,
  <lb/>adeo ut ratio spatii alicujus h<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>perbolici <formula>BADEF</formula> ad parallelogra<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>um <formula>ADEG</formula> sit ut <formula>\frac{x^{m+1}}{m+1}+\frac{\infty^{-m-1}}{-m-1}</formula> ad
  <formula>x^{m+1}</formula>, sive neglecto <formula>\frac{x^{m+1}}{m+1}</formula> ut <formula>\frac{\infty^{-m-1}}{-m-1}</formula> ad <formula>x^{m+1}</formula>, atque adeo longe alia <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> ratione 1 ad <formula>m+1</formula>.
  <lb/>Alterum, in quo <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118771167">Wallisius</rs> fallitur, hoc est, quod unitatem ad numerum negativum <abbr>ex. gr.</abbr> 1 ad <formula>-1</formula>, et propter
  <lb/>ea spatium h<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>perbolicum Cubicale ad parallelogra<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>um inscriptum dicit habere rationem plusquam infini<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tam, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> omnia falsissima sunt; nam nec spatium h<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>perbolicum Cubicale ad parallelogra<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>um inscri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ptum habet rationem plusquam infinitam, sed simpliciter infinitam, nec eam quam habet 1 ad <formula>-1</formula>,
  <lb/>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> potius est ratio complementi h<choice><orig><g ref="#ydots">ÿ</g></orig><reg>y</reg></choice>perbolici <formula>DCHE</formula> ad parallelogra<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>um <formula>ADEG</formula>,<!-- Das D ist intermediär. --> nec ratio 1 ad <formula>-1</formula>
  <lb/>est plus quam infinita, alias vicissim <formula>-1</formula> ad 1 haberet rationem minorem quam infinite parvam, cum ta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>men utraque ratio sit ratio <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualitatis, sed ut ita dicam negativa <abbr>h. e.</abbr> <choice rend="regFormula"><orig><formula>1.-1::-1.1</formula></orig><reg><formula>1:-1=-1:1</formula></reg></choice>, quod patet multi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>plicando extrema et media. Hinc est quod dubitem, an <abbr>P.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118937669">Grandus</rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118771167">Wallisium</rs> etiam hac in parte
  <lb/>defensurus sit, quocirca mallem scire, in quonam consistant ejus responsiones ad <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119062372">Varignonii</rs> <rs type="biblio">sche<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>diasma</rs>. <rs type="biblio">Mechanicam corporum fluidorum</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> te conscribi audio, quod si ita est, non leve capi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>et augmentum fama Tua pariter et res liter<add>ar</add>ia, cum nil nisi utile et elegans <rs type="biblio">libro</rs> hoc conten<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tum iri persuasus sim. <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1089923198">Verzaglia</rs> dudum profectus est <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2973783">Argentoratum</rs>, nec ex eo tempore
  <pb facs="1038113" n="3"/>
  <lb/>quicquam de eo cognovimus, salutem tamen Tuo nomine ipsi dum adhuc hic esset denuntiavi, quam
    <lb/>cum gratiarum actione l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tus accepit amice rogans, ut Te, si quando responsionem Tibi missurus
    <lb/>essem, vicissim salutare haud gravate vellem. <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1101972254">Thomasius</rs><!-- ToDo: Kontrollieren, ob die Person richtig indentifiziert ist --> <rs type="place" key="place_VER-englan">Anglus</rs> cras aut perendie proficisce<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tur <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2657896">Tigurum</rs> et inde in <rs type="place" key="place_KON-italie">Italiam</rs>, quamque Tibi se debere affirmavit ad <rs type="letter">literas</rs><!-- ToDo: Dieser Brief ist anscheinend nicht erhalten. In BIBB erfassen --> quasdam Tuas
    <lb/><rs type="letter">responsionem</rs><!-- ToDo: Dieser Brief ist anscheinend nicht erhalten. In BIBB erfassen --> ipsemet perlaturus est; quin te bona utentem valetudine reperiat, non dubito;
  <lb/>hanc ut Deus Tibi non solum per istius nuper incepti sed et plurimorum insequentium a<choice><orig><g ref="#nn">n̄</g></orig><reg>nn</reg></choice>o<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum decursum clementer conservet, su<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>a votorum meorum est.</p>
<closer>Vale igitur quam optime et
